[div class=p 
	[em 
		"Rockman no Constancy
	]em
	" is a very extensive ROM hack of 
	[em 
		"Mega Man 2
	]em
	", with changes to the music, the graphics, the level design, and the characters. A couple of the powerups from the original game remain, which means that a number of techniques that can be done there can also be done here.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
